import { configureStore } from '@reduxjs/toolkit'
import filter from './slices/filterSlices'
import card from './slices/CardSlice'
import Snackscard from './slices/SnacksCardSlice'
import DrinksCard from './slices/DrinksCardSlice'
import NapitkiCard from './slices/Napitki'

export default configureStore({
  reducer: {
    filter,
    card,
    Snackscard,
    DrinksCard,
  },
})
